This project is an open-source, review-gated PPT workflow Skill.
It includes workflow instructions, validation scripts, local review pages,
and conversion tooling for generating editable PPT pages from structured
content and SVG page sources.

Attribution and source identification may appear in repository documents,
process HTML pages, review server pages, validation pages, and developer
workflow surfaces. The Skill should not add project branding to final client
deliverables by default unless the user explicitly requests it.
